<template>
    <v-app>
      <v-container>
        <v-tabs v-model="tab">
          <v-tab v-for="(tab, i) in tabs" :key="i">{{ tab.name }}</v-tab>
        </v-tabs>
        <v-tab-item v-for="(tab, i) in tabs" :key="i">
          <v-card>
            <v-card-text>{{ tab.content }}</v-card-text>
          </v-card>
        </v-tab-item>
      </v-container>
    </v-app>
  </template>
  
  <script>
  export default {
    data() {
      return {
        tab: 0,
        tabs: [
          {
            name: 'Tab 1',
            content: 'This is the content for Tab 1',
          },
          {
            name: 'Tab 2',
            content: 'This is the content for Tab 2',
          },
          {
            name: 'Tab 3',
            content: 'This is the content for Tab 3',
          },
        ],
      };
    },
  };
  </script>
